Tutorial for installing Snort on Kali Linux VM:

1. Open the terminal and edit your sources list with a text editor of your choice:
   sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list

2. To the file add:
   deb http://http.us.debian.org/debian/ bullseye non-free contrib main

3. save and exit ctrl+x and Y.

4. Then update
   sudo apt-get update

5. Install snort:
   sudo apt-get install snort

